snippet: Occupy protesters go after the Democratic Party, showing that they are equal opportunity agitators.
abstract: Occupy protesters go after the Democratic Party, showing that they are equal opportunity agitators.
lead_paragraph: In what Occupy the Caucus members called a symbolic "die-in," 12 protesters lay motionless on the lobby floor of the Renaissance Des Moines Savory Hotel Monday afternoon before getting arrested.

headline.main: Democrats Become Target of Occupy Protests
